    • __match

      protected boolean __match​(POJO other)
      Convienence method for subclass implementations wishing to implement one of the object lookup interfaces, which checks the response ids against each other. It is assumed that the multi child lookups will be using a composite key that includes the response id as well as another id from the Nessus API
      Parameters:
      other - the other

      the boolean
